程序包com.aylanetworks.agilelink.framework的说明

Core components of the Agile Link application framework.

This package the set of core classes used by the Agile Link application framework. Implementers should not need to modify these classes directly, but rather should customize behavior by deriving classes from some of the classes defined in this package.

The ViewModel class provides basic functionality for Device objects, and should be overridden for each type of device the application will support.

Implementers will also need to create a class derived from ViewModelProvider to create ViewModel objects of the appropriate type from AylaDevice objects.

The AMAPCore class is used to configure the application parameters, user information, and anything else needed to be set up before connecting to the Ayla network.
